item.dc:creator: @PaulT PaulT
item.description:
@PaulT wrote:

If you’re going to get an i5, get the 4690k and please, for the love of god, get a matching RAM kit. Also, that CPU cooler should be replaced with something better. Gigabyte is probably not the motherboard you want. You want Asus/ASrock, or MSI, in my opinion. For the 270x you probably want a bit beefier power supply, just in case. Also, spend a bit more and get a better monitor, you’re going to be looking at it all day.

Need’s some work.
